body.description: Furinno Turn-N-Tube multipurpose shelf features (1) unique structure: simple and stylish look is ideal as a decorative and home living essentials. Suitable for any rooms needing additional storage or display spaces. Designed to meet the demand of low cost but durable and efficient furniture. It is proven to be the most popular RTA furniture due to its functionality, price and the no hassle assembly. (2) smart Design: easy assembly and no tools required. A smart design that uses durable recycled PVC tubes and engineered medium density composite wood that withstand heavy weight. Just repeat the twist, turn and stack mechanism and the whole unit can be assembled within 10 minutes. Experience the fun of D-I-Y even with your kids. (3) The composite wood is manufactured in Malaysia and made from recycled materials of rubber trees. The manufacturing process complies with the Green rules of production. There is no foul smell, durable and the material is the most stable amongst the medium density composite woods. The PVC tube is made from recycled plastic and is tested for its durability. A simple attitude towards lifestyle is reflected directly on the design of Furinno furniture, creating a trend of simply nature. All the products are produced and assembled 100-percent in Malaysia with 95% - 100% recycled materials. Care instructions: wipe clean with clean damped cloth. Avoid using harsh chemicals. Pictures are for illustration purpose. All decor items are not included in this offer.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: About the Manufacturer Bridging innovation with simplistic furniture, Furinno brings modern designs to transform your home into a one-of-a-kind oasis that will surely assist the compact and space saving need for your home. Engineered with recycled Malaysian rubberwood, Furinno is committed to making home furnishing easy affordable, and unique while remaining sustainable in the process. Furinno Turn-N-Tube Collection Turn, Twist & Repeat! Furinno Turn-N-Tube Collection features the serenity of the Japanese living room lifestyle. These multifunctional tables and shelves are suitable for any room that need storage shelves, display, TV entertainment, or even kids room. The designs are simple and basic which fits into a modern stylish lifestyle. Modern color style. Stylish. Functional. Affordable. Easy to assemble.

Premium Quality Materials Manufactured from high quality particle board to ensure long product life span and enhanced durability. Rounded Edge Designed with round edges for added safety to reduce accidental injuries. Easy Assembly A smart design that you can experience the fun of assembly even with your kids. You do not need other tools to assemble. Extra Storage Space Two shelves at the bottom given sufficient storage room for easy organization and display.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, don't wobble, hold weight, neutral color, storage space
reviews.reviewText: The bed side tables are a fantastic addition to any bedroom. They are sturdy and hold up well over time, even with regular use. They are stable and level and don't wobble and hold weight well. Assembling them is a breeze and can be done in about 10 minutes, making them a great option for anyone who wants something functional without a lot of hassle.One of the most impressive things about these bed side tables is their affordability. They offer great value for the money, and it's hard to believe how much they cost considering their high quality and durability.The material used to make the tables hasn't chipped and scratched despite rough and tough use, I'm sure they will look great for years to come. Great for students on a budget. The neutral colors of gray and black make them versatile and easy to match with any decor style.The bed side tables are a great option for people on a budget who want to spruce up their bedroom decor. They are the perfect size to hold a lamp, phone, water bottle, and other small items that you might need within reach. The rounded corners make them safe and practical, as they won't accidentally poke or injure anyone.The addition of a storage shelf on the bottom of the tables provides extra space to store items like books or magazines, making them even more functional.Overall, I would highly recommend these bed side tables to anyone looking for a functional and affordable option that looks great in any bedroom. They are sturdy, easy to assemble, and provide excellent value for the money.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars WESOME VALUE, quick assembly, no worries!
reviews.reviewText: Awesome in every way!• The typical Amazon PRIME ordering system comes through again -- quick delivery, courteous service.INSTRUCTIONS• The shelving unit comes with an EXCELLENT set of easy to follow instructions. These include proper English spelling, grammar, and syntax. As a senior technical writer creating such instructions since the 1970s, I feel your pain when directions are less than intelligible. These instructions will make your day and help you make your shelf.THE SHELF• Six basic parts consist of four legs, a center shelf, and an upper shelf. These are made of sawdust and glue, right, with a nice veneer in your choice of colors and faux wood patterns. Pretty good quality for the price.• The hardware pieces are all grouped together in cellophane bags, and those come in one larger bag.• The directions predict about a 15-minute assembly time and encourage the reading of the instructions in their entirety BEFORE proceeding.• Get a smaller tipped Phillips screwdriver and a hammer to start the assembly.• It all goes together logically, follow the instructions.FINAL PRODUCT• Excellent, very cool. Fits the need perfectly.• The manufacturer claims that the shelf unit will hold 15 pounds (6,8 kilograms) on the top shelf, and 10 pounds (4,5 kilograms) on the mid-shelf. I don't know why anyone would put that much weight on it, but it should hold a few books, a laptop computer, etc., or a vase with water holding flowers, and more.GREAT SHELF! ENJOY!GET SOME!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cheap, but easy to assemble and very light
reviews.reviewText: Overall build quality of this piece is very poor. The engineered wood will start to bubble and chip as the product ages and the plastic legs will start to strip as it's assembled and disassembled. Overall though, it does the job reasonably well of providing a place to put keys/phone/alarm clock bedside. This piece is especially good for a smaller room where a full sized night stand may be too much or a college dorm. However, the build quality is very low and the materials are very cheap- do not count on holding onto this piece for more than a couple of years.Overall, a reasonably priced night stand substitute for small rooms or dorms that's probably just going to get thrown away during a move.
